text: Erëleta Memeti (born 30 June 1999) is a Kosovar footballer who plays as a midfielder and has appeared for the Kosovo women's national team. ==Career== Memeti has been capped for the Kosovo national team, appearing for the team during the UEFA Women's Euro 2021 qualifying cycle. ==References== ==External links== * * * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:Kosovan women's footballers Category:Kosovo women's international footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders
